SENATE SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4002
A bill to amend 2018 PA 338, entitled
"Earned sick time act,"
by amending the title and sections 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, and 12 (MCL
408.962, 408.963, 408.964, 408.965, 408.966, 408.967, 408.968, and
408.972) and by adding section 3a.
