21 civil action as provided in subsection (1)(a) on behalf of the
22 employee. The department may investigate and file a civil action
23 under subsection (1)(a) on behalf of all employees of that employer
24 who are similarly situated at the same work site and who have not
25 brought a civil action under subsection (1)(a). A worksite. Except
26 as otherwise provided under section 12, a contract or agreement
27 between the employer and the employee or any acceptance by the
28 employee of a paid or unpaid leave policy that provides fewer
29 rights or benefits than provided by this act is void and
GSS H00951'25 (S-3) abhr40

